<body>
  <main>
      <div class="container-fluid">
          <div class="row">
              <div class="col-sm-6 col-sm-offset-1 lc">
                  <h1><%= @recent.title %></h1>
                  <div class="row">
                      <div class="col-sm-12 postertag">
                          <%= image_tag @recent.author.name, class: 'img-circle', id:'postersmall'%>
                          <h5> <%= @recent.author.name %> <small>on <a href="">
                            <%= @recent.created_at.strftime("%A, %d %b %Y %l:%M %p") %></a></small></h5>
                      </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="row">
                      <div class="col-sm-12">
                          <p> <%= simple_format(@recent.body) %></p>
                      </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="row">
                      <div class="col-sm-12 glyph">
                          <div class="btn-group" role="group" aria-label="...">
                              <button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-xs"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-comment" aria-hidden="true"></span></button>
                              <button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-xs">Read Comments</button>
                          </div>
                          <div class="btn-group" role="group" aria-label="...">
                              <button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-xs"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-cloud-upload" aria-hidden="true"></span></button>
                              <button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-xs">Read Later</button>
                          </div>
                          <div class="btn-group" role="group" aria-label="...">
                              <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-xs"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share" aria-hidden="true"></span></button>
                              <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-xs">Share This Post</button>
                          </div>
                      </div>
                  </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-sm-4 rc">
                  <%= image_tag @recent.author.name, class: 'img-circle center-block', id:'poster'%>
                  <h4 class="text-center"><%= @recent.author.name.upcase %></h4>
                  <p class="text-center"><small>
          <a href="http://www.twitter.com">twitter</a> |
          <a href="http://www.facebook.com">facebook</a> |
          <a href="http://www.instagram.com">instagram</a>
        </small></p>
                  <div class="row ad">
                      <div class="col-sm-12 ad">
                        <%= image_tag "ad"+rand(6).to_s, class: 'img-responsive', id:'adpic'%>
                      </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="row">
                      <div class="col-sm-12">
                          <p class="text-right"><small><a href="">About This Ad</a></small></p>
                      </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="row">
                      <div class="col-sm-12">
                          <h4>Sidebar Section Heading</h4>
                          <h5><small>Bacon ipsum dolor amet sausage shank dolore, occaecat ea ribeye commodo short loin tail proident t-bone aliqua ipsum ham hock voluptate. Flank leberkas sint tri-tip turducken veniam, aliquip laborum strip steak sunt est ut sed. Dolor culpa prosciutto adipisicing quis, irure brisket. Quis excepteur strip steak, reprehenderit eu ball tip picanha.</small></h5>
                      </div>
                  </div>
              </div>
          </div>
      </div>
  </main>

</body>

</html>
